Why this would make "conversational hypnosis" more effective

Hyper-personalization of language:    AI could select metaphors that resonate specifically with your experience (for example, if the model "knows" that you associate calm with the sea, not with a forest).
Precise timing:                       Analysis of physiological signals would allow suggestions to be administered at moments of natural de-escalation (microtrances, fatigue, relaxation).
